    "description": "<strong>Polyrun</strong> is an action packed, indie runner experience! Competitive <strong>local multiplayer</strong>, In depth <strong>character customization</strong>, endless <strong>singleplayer</strong>, <strong>power ups</strong> and more. Test your agility and reflexes, and climb the <strong>leaderboard</strong> ranks.<br><br><strong>Character Customization:</strong><br>Earn in-game currency, <i>Polycoin</i>, by playing and earning high scores. No microtransactions necessary! With your earned <i>Polycoin</i>, you can purchase cosmetic items from the customization store! Give your <i>Polyrunner</i> a makeover, anything from hats, glasses and shirts, to gloves, shoes, tails and more!<br><br><strong>Endless Singleplayer:</strong><br>This mode is your traditional, endless runner experience! Weaving your customized <i>Polyrunner</i> between the obstacles, grabbing score cubes and obtaining power ups! Keep practising at your agility and reflexes, and see your username climb the leaderboards!<br><br><strong>Local Multiplayer:</strong><br>Get competitive in the local multiplayer versus mode! Grab a friend and be the best at chasing down those precious score cubes! Use power ups to aid yourself, or to impair your opponent! One round simply not enough? Try the best out of three <strong>Tournament mode!</strong><br><br><strong>Polyrun</strong> was proudly created in Christchurch, New Zealand by the team at <strong>Aurora Gameworks.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1097870/extras/a25489c89f7beab9d4608e3671008588.webp?t=1592667236\" width=300 height=59 /></span>",
